cpanurl

INSTALLATION

  curl -kL https://raw.github.com/yuki-kimoto/cpanurl/master/script/cpanurl > cpanurl
  chmod +x cpanurl

or
  cpan App-cpanurl
  
Examples:

  cpanurl Mojolicious 3.82
  
  You can get output http://cpan.metacpan.org/authors/id/S/SR/SRI/Mojolicious-3.82.tar.gz

